WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.006
Digital stalking is when you email, call, and text the same customer about

00:00:04.056 --> 00:00:08.062
the same thing inside an hour. It is well-intentioned and it feels like

00:00:08.112 --> 00:00:12.118
overkill to them. Pick one channel and give the customer time to respond.
